<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.101.113090.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Pestalotiopsis chamaeropis (NTUPPMCC 21 - 054 = CD 09) A the original habitat of Pestalotiopsis chamaeropis; the stroma of Ophiocordyceps sp. B top view (left) and bottom view (right) of the colony on potato dextrose agar (PDA) after incubation for seven days C conidiomata on carnation leaf D, E conidiogenous cells and immature conidia F-I conidia. Scale bars: 250 μm (C); 20 μm (D-I)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/976791" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

